{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm here today"},{"time":3000,"text":"to start a revolution."},{"time":5000,"text":"Now before you get up in arms,"},{"time":7000,"text":"or you break into song,"},{"time":9000,"text":"or you pick a favorite color,"},{"time":11000,"text":"I want to define what I mean by revolution."},{"time":14000,"text":"By revolution,"},{"time":16000,"text":"I mean a drastic and far-reaching change"},{"time":19000,"text":"in the way we think and behave --"},{"time":22000,"text":"the way we think and the way we behave."},{"time":25000,"text":"Now why, Steve, why do we need a revolution?"},{"time":28000,"text":"We need a revolution"},{"time":30000,"text":"because things aren't working; they're just not working."},{"time":33000,"text":"And that makes me really sad"},{"time":35000,"text":"because I'm sick and tired of things not working."},{"time":38000,"text":"You know, I'm sick and tired of us not living up to our potential."},{"time":41000,"text":"I'm sick and tired of us being last."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44000,"text":"And we are last place in so many things --"},{"time":47000,"text":"for example, social factors."},{"time":50000,"text":"We're last place in Europe in innovation."},{"time":53000,"text":"There we are right at the end, right at the bottom,"},{"time":56000,"text":"last place as a culture that doesn't value innovation."},{"time":59000,"text":"We're last place in health care,"},{"time":61000,"text":"and that's important for a sense of well-being."},{"time":63000,"text":"And there we are, not just last in the E.U.,"},{"time":65000,"text":"we're last in Europe, at the very bottom."},{"time":67000,"text":"And worst of all,"},{"time":69000,"text":"it just came out three weeks ago, many of you have seen it, The Economist."},{"time":72000,"text":"We're the saddest place on Earth,"},{"time":75000,"text":"relative to GDP per capita --"},{"time":77000,"text":"the saddest place on Earth."},{"time":79000,"text":"That's social. Let's look at education."},{"time":82000,"text":"Where do we rank three weeks ago"},{"time":84000,"text":"in another report by the OECD?"},{"time":86000,"text":"Last in reading, math and science. Last."},{"time":89000,"text":"Business:"},{"time":91000,"text":"The lowest perception in the E.U."},{"time":93000,"text":"that entrepreneurs provide benefits to society."},{"time":96000,"text":"Why as a result, what happens?"},{"time":98000,"text":"The lowest percentage of entrepreneurs starting businesses."},{"time":101000,"text":"And this is despite the fact"},{"time":103000,"text":"that everybody knows that small business"},{"time":105000,"text":"is the engine of economies."},{"time":107000,"text":"We hire the most people; we create the most taxes."},{"time":110000,"text":"So if our engine's broken, guess what?"},{"time":113000,"text":"Last in Europe GDP per capita."},{"time":116000,"text":"Last."},{"time":118000,"text":"So it's no surprise, guys, that 62 percent of Bulgarians"},{"time":121000,"text":"are not optimistic about the future."},{"time":123000,"text":"We're unhappy, we have bad education,"},{"time":125000,"text":"and we have the worst businesses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"And these are facts, guys."},{"time":130000,"text":"This isn't story tale; it's not make-believe."},{"time":133000,"text":"It's not."},{"time":135000,"text":"It's not a conspiracy I have got against Bulgaria. These are facts."},{"time":138000,"text":"So I think it should be really, really clear"},{"time":140000,"text":"that our system is broken."},{"time":142000,"text":"The way we think, the way we behave,"},{"time":144000,"text":"our operating system of behaving is broken."},{"time":146000,"text":"We need a drastic change in the way we think and behave"},{"time":149000,"text":"to transform Bulgaria for the better,"},{"time":151000,"text":"for ourselves, for our friends,"},{"time":153000,"text":"for our family and for our future."},{"time":155000,"text":"How did this happen?"},{"time":157000,"text":"Let's be positive now. We're going to get positive. How did this happen?"},{"time":160000,"text":"I think we're last because --"},{"time":162000,"text":"and this is going to be drastic to some of you --"},{"time":164000,"text":"because we are handicapping ourselves."},{"time":166000,"text":"We're holding ourselves back"},{"time":168000,"text":"because we don't value play."},{"time":170000,"text":"I said \"play,\" all right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"In case some of you forgot what play is, this is what play looks like."},{"time":175000,"text":"Babies play, kids play,"},{"time":177000,"text":"adults play."},{"time":179000,"text":"We don't value play."},{"time":181000,"text":"In fact, we devalue play."},{"time":183000,"text":"And we devalue it in three areas."},{"time":185000,"text":"Let's go back to the same three areas."},{"time":187000,"text":"Social: 45 years of what?"},{"time":189000,"text":"Of communism --"},{"time":191000,"text":"of valuing the society and the state over the individual"},{"time":194000,"text":"and squashing, inadvertently,"},{"time":196000,"text":"creativity, individual self-expression and innovation."},{"time":200000,"text":"And instead, what do we value?"},{"time":202000,"text":"Because it's shown"},{"time":204000,"text":"the way we apply, generate and use knowledge"},{"time":208000,"text":"is affected by our social and institutional context,"},{"time":210000,"text":"which told us what in communism?"},{"time":212000,"text":"To be serious."},{"time":214000,"text":"To be really, really serious."},{"time":216000,"text":"It did."},{"time":218000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":222000,"text":"Be serious."},{"time":224000,"text":"I can't tell you how many times I've been scolded in the park"},{"time":227000,"text":"for letting my kids play on the ground."},{"time":231000,"text":"Heaven forbid they play in the dirt, the kal,"},{"time":234000,"text":"or even worse, lokvi, water -- that will kill them."},{"time":237000,"text":"I have been told by babas and dyados"},{"time":239000,"text":"that we shouldn't let our kids play so much"},{"time":242000,"text":"because life is serious"},{"time":244000,"text":"and we need to train them for the seriousness of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"We have a serious meme running through."},{"time":249000,"text":"It's a social gene running through us."},{"time":251000,"text":"It's a serious gene."},{"time":253000,"text":"It's 45 years of it"},{"time":255000,"text":"that's created what I call the \"baba factor.\""},{"time":257000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":259000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":261000,"text":"And here's how it works."},{"time":263000,"text":"Step one: woman says, \"I want to have a baby. Iskam baby.\""},{"time":266000,"text":"Step two: we get the baby. Woohoo!"},{"time":268000,"text":"But then what happens in step three?"},{"time":270000,"text":"I want to go back to work"},{"time":272000,"text":"because I need to further my career or I just want to go have coffees."},{"time":275000,"text":"I'm going to give bebko to baba."},{"time":278000,"text":"But we need to remember"},{"time":280000,"text":"that baba's been infected by the serious meme for 45 years."},{"time":283000,"text":"So what happens?"},{"time":285000,"text":"She passes that virus on to baby,"},{"time":288000,"text":"and it takes a really, really, really long time -- as the redwood trees --"},{"time":292000,"text":"for that serious meme"},{"time":294000,"text":"to get out of our operating system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297000,"text":"What happens then?"},{"time":299000,"text":"It goes into education where we have an antiquated education system"},{"time":302000,"text":"that has little changed for 100 years,"},{"time":304000,"text":"that values rote learning,"},{"time":306000,"text":"memorization and standardization,"},{"time":308000,"text":"and devalues self-expression, self-exploration,"},{"time":311000,"text":"questioning, creativity and play."},{"time":313000,"text":"It's a crap system."},{"time":315000,"text":"True story: I went looking for a school for my kid."},{"time":319000,"text":"We went to this prestigious little school"},{"time":321000,"text":"and they say they're going to study math 10 times a week"},{"time":323000,"text":"and science eight times a week"},{"time":325000,"text":"and reading five times a day and all this stuff."},{"time":327000,"text":"And we said, \"Well what about play and recess?\""},{"time":330000,"text":"And they said, \"Ha. There won't be a single moment in the schedule.\""},{"time":333000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":335000,"text":"And we said, \"He's five.\""},{"time":337000,"text":"What a crime. What a crime."},{"time":339000,"text":"And it's a crime"},{"time":341000,"text":"that our education system is so serious because education is serious"},{"time":344000,"text":"that we're creating mindless, robotic workers"},{"time":346000,"text":"to put bolts in pre-drilled holes."},{"time":348000,"text":"But I'm sorry, the problems of today"},{"time":350000,"text":"are not the problems of the Industrial Revolution."},{"time":352000,"text":"We need adaptability,"},{"time":354000,"text":"the ability to learn how to be creative and innovative."},{"time":357000,"text":"We don't need mechanized workers."},{"time":359000,"text":"But no, now our meme goes into work where we don't value play."},{"time":362000,"text":"We create robotic workers that we treat like assets,"},{"time":365000,"text":"to lever and just throw away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"What are qualities of a Bulgarian work?"},{"time":370000,"text":"Autocratic --"},{"time":372000,"text":"do what I say because I'm the chef."},{"time":374000,"text":"I'm the boss and I know better than you."},{"time":376000,"text":"Untrusting -- you're obviously a criminal, so I'm going to install cameras."},{"time":379000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":381000,"text":"Controlling --"},{"time":383000,"text":"you're obviously an idiot, so I'm going to make"},{"time":385000,"text":"a zillion little processes for you to follow so you don't step out of the box."},{"time":388000,"text":"So they're restrictive -- don't use your mobile phone,"},{"time":390000,"text":"don't use your laptop, don't search the Internet,"},{"time":392000,"text":"don't be on I.M."},{"time":394000,"text":"That's somehow unprofessional and bad."},{"time":396000,"text":"And at the end of the day, it's unfulfilling"},{"time":398000,"text":"because you're controlled, you're restricted, you're not valued"},{"time":401000,"text":"and you're not having any fun."},{"time":403000,"text":"In social, in education and in our business,"},{"time":405000,"text":"don't value play."},{"time":407000,"text":"And that's why we're last,"},{"time":409000,"text":"because we don't value play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"And you can say, \"That's ridiculous, Steve. What a dumb idea."},{"time":414000,"text":"It can't be because of play."},{"time":416000,"text":"Just play, that's a stupid thing.\""},{"time":418000,"text":"We have the serious meme in us."},{"time":420000,"text":"Well I'm going to say no."},{"time":422000,"text":"And I will prove it to you in the next part of the speech --"},{"time":425000,"text":"that play is the catalyst, it is the revolution,"},{"time":428000,"text":"that we can use to transform Bulgaria for the better."},{"time":431000,"text":"Play:"},{"time":433000,"text":"our brains"},{"time":435000,"text":"are hardwired for play."},{"time":437000,"text":"Evolution has selected,"},{"time":439000,"text":"over millions and billions of years,"},{"time":442000,"text":"for play in animals and in humans."},{"time":445000,"text":"And you know what?"},{"time":447000,"text":"Evolution does a really, really good job"},{"time":449000,"text":"of deselecting traits that aren't advantageous to us"},{"time":452000,"text":"and selecting traits for competitive advantage."},{"time":455000,"text":"Nature isn't stupid, and it selected for play."},{"time":458000,"text":"Throughout the animal kingdom, for example:"},{"time":460000,"text":"ants. Ants play."},{"time":462000,"text":"Maybe you didn't know that."},{"time":464000,"text":"But when they're playing,"},{"time":466000,"text":"they're learning the social order and dynamics of things."},{"time":468000,"text":"Rats play, but what you might not have known"},{"time":470000,"text":"is that rats that play more"},{"time":472000,"text":"have bigger brains"},{"time":474000,"text":"and they learn tasks better,"},{"time":476000,"text":"skills."},{"time":478000,"text":"Kittens play. We all know kittens play."},{"time":480000,"text":"But what you may not know"},{"time":482000,"text":"is that kittens deprived of play"},{"time":485000,"text":"are unable to interact socially."},{"time":487000,"text":"They can still hunt, but they can't be social."},{"time":490000,"text":"Bears play."},{"time":492000,"text":"But what you may not know"},{"time":494000,"text":"is that bears that play more survive longer."},{"time":497000,"text":"It's not the bears that learn how to fish better."},{"time":499000,"text":"It's the ones that play more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"And a final really interesting study --"},{"time":504000,"text":"it's been shown, a correlation"},{"time":506000,"text":"between play and brain size."},{"time":508000,"text":"The more you play, the bigger the brains there are."},{"time":511000,"text":"Dolphins, pretty big brains, play a lot."},{"time":514000,"text":"But who do you think"},{"time":516000,"text":"with the biggest brains are the biggest players?"},{"time":519000,"text":"Yours truly: humans."},{"time":521000,"text":"Kids play, we play --"},{"time":523000,"text":"of every nationality, of every race,"},{"time":525000,"text":"of every color, of every religion."},{"time":527000,"text":"It's a universal thing -- we play."},{"time":529000,"text":"And it's not just kids, it's adults too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532000,"text":"Really cool term: neoteny --"},{"time":534000,"text":"the retention of play and juvenile traits in adults."},{"time":537000,"text":"And who are the biggest neotenists?"},{"time":539000,"text":"Humans. We play sports."},{"time":541000,"text":"We do it for fun, or as Olympians, or as professionals."},{"time":543000,"text":"We play musical instruments."},{"time":545000,"text":"We dance, we kiss, we sing,"},{"time":547000,"text":"we just goof around."},{"time":549000,"text":"We're designed by nature to play"},{"time":552000,"text":"from birth to old age."},{"time":555000,"text":"We're designed to do that continuously --"},{"time":558000,"text":"to play and play a lot"},{"time":560000,"text":"and not stop playing."},{"time":562000,"text":"It is a huge benefit."},{"time":565000,"text":"Just like there's benefits to animals,"},{"time":567000,"text":"there's benefits to humans."},{"time":569000,"text":"For example, it's been shown"},{"time":571000,"text":"to stimulate neural growth in the amygdala,"},{"time":573000,"text":"in the area where it controls emotions."},{"time":575000,"text":"It's been shown to promote pre-frontal cortex development"},{"time":578000,"text":"where a lot of cognition is happening."},{"time":580000,"text":"As a result, what happens?"},{"time":582000,"text":"We develop more emotional maturity if we play more."},{"time":585000,"text":"We develop better decision-making ability"},{"time":587000,"text":"if we play more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589000,"text":"These guys are facts."},{"time":591000,"text":"It's not fiction, it's not story tales, it's not make-believe;"},{"time":593000,"text":"it's cold, hard science."},{"time":595000,"text":"These are the benefits to play."},{"time":598000,"text":"It is a genetic birthright that we have,"},{"time":601000,"text":"like walking or speaking or seeing."},{"time":604000,"text":"And if we handicap ourselves with play,"},{"time":606000,"text":"we handicap ourselves"},{"time":608000,"text":"as if we would with any other birthright that we have."},{"time":610000,"text":"We hold ourselves back."},{"time":614000,"text":"Little exercise just for a second:"},{"time":616000,"text":"close your eyes"},{"time":618000,"text":"and try to imagine a world without play."},{"time":621000,"text":"Imagine a world without theater, without the arts,"},{"time":624000,"text":"without song, without dancing,"},{"time":627000,"text":"without soccer, without football,"},{"time":629000,"text":"without laughter."},{"time":631000,"text":"What does this world look like?"},{"time":633000,"text":"It's pretty bleak."},{"time":635000,"text":"It's pretty glum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637000,"text":"Now imagine your workplace."},{"time":639000,"text":"Is it fun? Is it playful?"},{"time":641000,"text":"Or maybe the workplace of your friends -- here we're forward thinking."},{"time":644000,"text":"Is it fun? Is it playful?"},{"time":646000,"text":"Or is it crap? Is it autocratic, controlling,"},{"time":649000,"text":"restrictive and untrusting and unfulfilling?"},{"time":654000,"text":"We have this concept"},{"time":656000,"text":"that the opposite of play is work."},{"time":659000,"text":"We even feel guilty if we're seen playing at work."},{"time":662000,"text":"\"Oh, my colleagues see me laughing. I must not have enough work,\""},{"time":665000,"text":"or, \"Oh, I've got to hide because my boss might see me."},{"time":668000,"text":"He's going to think I'm not working hard.\""},{"time":671000,"text":"But I have news for you: our thinking is backwards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673000,"text":"The opposite of play"},{"time":675000,"text":"is not work."},{"time":677000,"text":"The opposite of play"},{"time":679000,"text":"is depression. It's depression."},{"time":682000,"text":"In fact,"},{"time":684000,"text":"play improves our work."},{"time":686000,"text":"Just like there's benefits for humans and animals,"},{"time":688000,"text":"there's benefits for play at work."},{"time":690000,"text":"For example, it stimulates creativity."},{"time":694000,"text":"It increases our openness to change."},{"time":697000,"text":"It improves our ability to learn."},{"time":699000,"text":"It provides a sense of purpose and mastery --"},{"time":701000,"text":"two key motivational things"},{"time":703000,"text":"that increase productivity,"},{"time":705000,"text":"through play."},{"time":707000,"text":"So before you start thinking of play as just not serious,"},{"time":710000,"text":"play doesn't mean frivolous."},{"time":712000,"text":"You know, the professional athlete that loves skiing,"},{"time":714000,"text":"he's serious about it, but he loves it."},{"time":717000,"text":"He's having fun, he's in the groove, he's in the flow."},{"time":720000,"text":"A doctor might be serious,"},{"time":722000,"text":"but laughter's still a great medicine."},{"time":726000,"text":"Our thinking is backwards."},{"time":728000,"text":"We shouldn't be feeling guilty."},{"time":730000,"text":"We should be celebrating play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"Quick example from the corporate world."},{"time":734000,"text":"FedEx, easy motto: people, service, profit."},{"time":737000,"text":"If you treat your people like people, if you treat them great,"},{"time":740000,"text":"they're happier, they're fulfilled, they have a sense of mastery and purpose."},{"time":743000,"text":"What happens? They give better service --"},{"time":745000,"text":"not worse, but better."},{"time":747000,"text":"And when customers call for service"},{"time":749000,"text":"and they're dealing with happy people that can make decisions and are fulfilled,"},{"time":752000,"text":"how do the customers feel? They feel great."},{"time":754000,"text":"And what do great customers do, great-feeling customers?"},{"time":757000,"text":"They buy more of your service and they tell more of their friends,"},{"time":759000,"text":"which leads to more profit."},{"time":761000,"text":"People, service, profit."},{"time":763000,"text":"Play increases productivity, not decreases."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766000,"text":"And you're going to say,"},{"time":768000,"text":"\"Gee, that can work for FedEx out there in the United States,"},{"time":770000,"text":"but it can't work in Bulgaria."},{"time":772000,"text":"No way. We're different.\""},{"time":774000,"text":"It does work in Bulgaria, you guys. Two reasons."},{"time":776000,"text":"One, play is universal."},{"time":778000,"text":"There's nothing weird about Bulgarians that we can't play,"},{"time":781000,"text":"besides the serious meme that we have to kick out."},{"time":783000,"text":"Two, I've tried it. I've tried at Sciant."},{"time":786000,"text":"When I got there, we had zero happy customers."},{"time":788000,"text":"Not one customer would refer us."},{"time":790000,"text":"I asked them all."},{"time":792000,"text":"We had marginal profit -- I did."},{"time":794000,"text":"We had marginal profits,"},{"time":796000,"text":"and we had unhappy stakeholders."},{"time":798000,"text":"Through some basic change,"},{"time":800000,"text":"change like improving transparency,"},{"time":803000,"text":"change like promoting self-direction"},{"time":805000,"text":"and collaboration, encouraging collaboration,"},{"time":808000,"text":"not autocracy,"},{"time":810000,"text":"the things like having a results-focus."},{"time":812000,"text":"I don't care when you get in in the morning. I don't care when you leave."},{"time":815000,"text":"I care that your customer and your team is happy"},{"time":817000,"text":"and you're organized with that."},{"time":819000,"text":"Why do I care if you get in at nine o'clock?"},{"time":821000,"text":"Basically promoting fun."},{"time":823000,"text":"Through promoting fun and a great environment,"},{"time":826000,"text":"we were able to transform Sciant"},{"time":828000,"text":"and, in just three short years --"},{"time":830000,"text":"sounds like a long time, but change is slow --"},{"time":832000,"text":"every customer, from zero to every customer referring us,"},{"time":835000,"text":"above average profits for the industry"},{"time":837000,"text":"and happy stakeholders."},{"time":839000,"text":"And you can say, \"Well how do you know they're happy?\""},{"time":841000,"text":"Well we did win, every year that we entered,"},{"time":843000,"text":"one of the rankings for best employer for small business."},{"time":846000,"text":"Independent analysis from anonymous employees"},{"time":848000,"text":"on their surveys."},{"time":850000,"text":"It does, and it can, work in Bulgaria."},{"time":852000,"text":"There's nothing holding us back,"},{"time":854000,"text":"except our own mentality about play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"So some steps that we can take -- to finish up --"},{"time":860000,"text":"how to make this revolution through play."},{"time":862000,"text":"First of all, you have to believe me."},{"time":864000,"text":"If you don't believe me,"},{"time":866000,"text":"well just go home and think about it some more or something."},{"time":868000,"text":"Second of all, if you don't have the feeling of play in you,"},{"time":871000,"text":"you need to rediscover play."},{"time":873000,"text":"Whatever it was that as a kid you used to enjoy,"},{"time":875000,"text":"that you enjoyed only six months ago,"},{"time":877000,"text":"but now that you've got that promotion you can't enjoy,"},{"time":879000,"text":"because you feel like you have to be serious,"},{"time":881000,"text":"rediscover it."},{"time":883000,"text":"I don't care if it's mountain biking or reading a book or playing a game."},{"time":885000,"text":"Rediscover that"},{"time":887000,"text":"because you're the leaders,"},{"time":889000,"text":"the innovation leaders, the thought leaders."},{"time":891000,"text":"You're the ones that have to go back to the office"},{"time":893000,"text":"or talk to your friends"},{"time":895000,"text":"and ignite the fire of change in the play revolution."},{"time":898000,"text":"You guys have to, and if you're not feeling it,"},{"time":900000,"text":"your colleagues, your employees, aren't going to feel it."},{"time":903000,"text":"You've got to go back and say, \"Hey, I'm going to trust you.\""},{"time":906000,"text":"Weird concept: I hired you; I should trust you."},{"time":909000,"text":"I'm going to let you make decisions. I'm going to empower you,"},{"time":912000,"text":"and I'm going to delegate to the lowest level, rather than the top."},{"time":915000,"text":"I'm going to encourage constructive criticism."},{"time":918000,"text":"I'm going to let you challenge authority."},{"time":920000,"text":"Because it's by challenging the way things are always done"},{"time":923000,"text":"is that we are able to break out of the rut that we're in"},{"time":925000,"text":"and create innovative solutions"},{"time":927000,"text":"to problems of today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":929000,"text":"We're not always right as leaders."},{"time":931000,"text":"We're going to eradicate fear."},{"time":933000,"text":"Fear is the enemy of play."},{"time":936000,"text":"And we're going to do things"},{"time":938000,"text":"like eliminate restrictions."},{"time":940000,"text":"You know what, let them use their mobile phone"},{"time":942000,"text":"for personal calls -- heaven forbid."},{"time":945000,"text":"Let them be on the Internet."},{"time":947000,"text":"Let them be on instant messengers."},{"time":950000,"text":"Let them take long lunches."},{"time":954000,"text":"Lunch is like the recess for work."},{"time":956000,"text":"It's when you go out in the world"},{"time":958000,"text":"and you recharge your brain, you meet your friends,"},{"time":960000,"text":"you have a beer, you have some food, you talk,"},{"time":963000,"text":"you get some synergy of ideas"},{"time":965000,"text":"that maybe you wouldn't have had before."},{"time":967000,"text":"Let them do it. Give them some freedom,"},{"time":970000,"text":"and in general, let them play. Let them have fun at the workplace."},{"time":973000,"text":"We spend so much of our lives at the workplace,"},{"time":976000,"text":"and it's supposed to be, what, a miserable grind,"},{"time":978000,"text":"so that 20 years from now, we wake up and say, \"Is this it?"},{"time":981000,"text":"Is that all there was?\""},{"time":983000,"text":"Unacceptable. Nepriemliv."},{"time":985000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":988000,"text":"So in summary,"},{"time":990000,"text":"we need a drastic change"},{"time":992000,"text":"in the way we think and behave,"},{"time":994000,"text":"but we don't need"},{"time":996000,"text":"a workers' revolution."},{"time":999000,"text":"We don't need a workers' revolution."},{"time":1001000,"text":"What we need"},{"time":1003000,"text":"is a players' uprising."},{"time":1005000,"text":"What we need is a players' uprising."},{"time":1008000,"text":"What we need is a players' uprising."},{"time":1010000,"text":"Seriously, we need to band together."},{"time":1012000,"text":"Today is the start of the uprising."},{"time":1014000,"text":"But what you need to do"},{"time":1016000,"text":"is fan the flames of the revolution."},{"time":1018000,"text":"You need to go and share your ideas and your success stories"},{"time":1021000,"text":"of what worked"},{"time":1023000,"text":"about reinvigorating our lives, our schools,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"and our work with play;"},{"time":1028000,"text":"about how play promotes"},{"time":1030000,"text":"a sense of promise and self-fulfillment;"},{"time":1033000,"text":"of how play promotes innovation and productivity,"},{"time":1037000,"text":"and, ultimately, how play creates meaning."},{"time":1041000,"text":"Because we can't do it alone. We have to do it together,"},{"time":1044000,"text":"and together, if we do this and share these ideas on play,"},{"time":1047000,"text":"we can transform Bulgaria for the better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1051000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1053000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}